HEADWORD: Gazet
<hw>Ga*zet</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[It. <ets>gazeta</ets>,
<ets>gazzetta</ets>, prob. dim. of L. <ets>gaza</ets> royal
treasure.]</ety> <def>A Venetian coin, worth about three English
farthings, or one and a half cents.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

